# Snap applications. Bases/runtimes (core*, gnome-*, mesa-*, gtk-common-
# themes, bare, snapd) install automatically as dependencies — never list
# them here.
# Format: name [--classic] [@group]   — @group gates on that apt group's
# host-conf toggle; no @group = always (dev-on-VM baseline).
tailscale                               # node networking — always
imgcat                                  # tiny CLI — always
canonical-livepatch                     # needs 'pro attach' before it does anything
chromium @apps
# firefox @apps          # dropped — owner does not use (chromium covers browser/headless)
# thunderbird @apps      # dropped — owner does not use
evince @apps
cups @apps                              # printing is driverless IPP once cups present
snap-store @desktop
multipass @apps                         # VM manager — pointless inside a VM
# --- dropped / flagged ---
# bruno                         DROPPED 2026-06-05 (also dropped as deb)
# hover                         FLAGGED: abandoned flutter-desktop tool
# wine-platform-5-stable        FLAGGED: wine comes from winehq apt repo now
# wine-platform-runtime         FLAGGED: see above
